#~ "prefix to downstream (e.g. LAN) interfaces.</li> <li><strong>hybrid mode</"
#~ "strong>: Router does both server+relay; extends upstream config and "
#~ "prefix downstream, and uses <abbr title=\"Prefix Delegation\">PD</abbr> "
#~ "locally.</li></ul>"
